  ${
    pltletr.b $e |- B = ( Base ` K ) $.
    pltletr.l $e |- L = ( le ` K ) $.
    pltletr.s $e |- S = ( lt ` K ) $.
    $( Transitive law for chained less-than and less-than-or-equal.  (Th.
       ~ psssstr analog.) $)
    pltletr $p |- ( ( K e. Poset /\ ( X e. B /\ Y e. B /\ Z e. B ) )
